item.title: CVE-2020-2282|2024-08-04T07:01:41.185Z -- jenkins%20project -- jenkins%20implied%20labels%20plugin
item.description: Jenkins Implied Labels Plugin 0.6 and earlier does not perform a permission check in an HTTP endpoint, allowing attackers with Overall/Read permission to configure the plugin.
